metadata.name: $CHECKERS #1
metadata.description: Checks Checkers is the first ever on-chain Checkers NFT game, in which each NFT token is totally unique in the way the game is developed and the strategies develop. The Checks Checkers NFT will display a unique simulated AI game between computer vs computer, in which the winner is totally dependant on the depth level of difficulty the AI computer has been programmed to play at.
